SupplyScout — Color & Design Theme
Use a DHL-inspired dark theme with warm yellow and red accents throughout the entire app.
Color Palette
Backgrounds

Page background: #0A0A08
Card/surface: #141410
Surface elevated: #1C1C16
Sidebar: #0E0E0C

Borders

Default border: #2A2A22
Border hover/light: #3A3A30

Text

Primary text: #F5F5F0 (warm white)
Secondary/muted text: #9A9A8E
Dim/placeholder text: #6A6A5E

Accent Colors

Primary accent (yellow): #FFCC00 — use for primary buttons, active states, highlights, badges, links, progress bars, focus rings
Primary hover: #FFD633
Secondary accent (red): #D40511 — use for destructive actions, alerts, upgrade CTAs, error states, important badges
Secondary hover: #E8222E
Headline gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFCC00, #E8222E)

Semantic Colors

Success/green: #22C55E
Warning: #F59E0B
Error: #D40511 (same as secondary accent)

Glow & Shadow Effects

Yellow glow: rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.12)
Yellow glow strong: rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.25)
Red glow: rgba(212, 5, 17, 0.15)
Green dim: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.12)
Card shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)

Button Styles

Primary button: bg #FFCC00, text #0A0A08 (dark text on yellow), hover #FFD633
Secondary/ghost button: bg transparent, border #2A2A22, text #F5F5F0, hover border #3A3A30
Destructive button: bg #D40511, text white, hover #E8222E
Button text on yellow backgrounds must always be dark (#0A0A08) for contrast

Typography

Headings: Plus Jakarta Sans, weights 700-800
Body: Plus Jakarta Sans, weights 400-500
Code/monospace/URLs: JetBrains Mono
Import: https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap

Usage Rules

All pricing "Most Popular" badges: yellow bg (#FFCC00) with dark text
Feature checkmarks in pricing cards: yellow (#FFCC00) not green
Section labels/eyebrows: yellow (#FFCC00)
Active sidebar nav item: yellow text or yellow left border indicator
Usage progress bars: yellow fill on dark track
Free tier upgrade banners: red accent (#D40511) background or border
Input focus state: yellow border with yellow glow ring
Loading spinners: yellow (#FFCC00)
Toast notifications: dark surface with yellow/red/green left border based on type